 />\n1.不反對通知書未過時<br />\n2.無証據入面有人對商店或途行進行破壞及傷害<br />\n<br />\n所以根本無任何原因放大批警員入內<br />\n嚇親巿民同攪到商戶無計做生意<br />\n<br />\n私人地方必需有手令先入得"},{"pid":"0378cd7879b0ec64d2b6e350d1f64d1a808f62c2","tid":1320034,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5G2vuZ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5G2vuZ7.png&h=5139ee97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d857da88014cb684370ad0ec1bb1b1b7b2e855ab","tid":1320034,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xhNSJkL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxhNSJkL.png&h=b47798ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e537673f9c3613f43ab6630853d9d44c8e69e3a6","tid":1320034,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQNvu0T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQNvu0T.png&h=5365c4db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"999846f9378831641901b9691cb7b2c2d184704a","tid":1320034,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/15/175416_9e8bbd0d3326f393505a108e00ff83e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2F175416_9e8bbd0d3326f393505a108e00ff83e7.png&h=8a2abae4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d33555c12c5bfc0b67df958da5994cf52b5183a","tid":1320034,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"老老實實shk仲未出律師信比黑警就知有鬼啦<br />\n點會個日嗰營業額損失會自己食曬"},{"pid":"28a5bdbd321b49a153fbcd14b26d0792cfded5d9","tid":1320034,"uid":6181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DopBqzz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum